ty-speak-on-the-general-election-encourage-voters-to-have-some-fucking-empathy-3770181"><div class="tdb-block-inner td-fix-index"><p> <a class="c-link c-link--focus-visible" href="https://www.nme.com/glastonbury-2024" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" data-stringify-link="https://www.nme.com/glastonbury-2024" data-sk="tooltip_parent">请返回<i data-stringify-type="italic">NME</i> ，了解 2024 年格拉斯顿伯里音乐节的最新</a>新闻、评论、采访、照片、谣言等。请<a class="c-link c-link--focus-visible" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/glastonbury-2024-liveblog-news-updates-reviews-rumours-photo-video-3769371" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" data-stringify-link="https://www.nme.com/news/music/glastonbury-2024-liveblog-news-updates-reviews-rumours-photo-video-3769371" data-sk="tooltip_parent">在此处查看<i data-stringify-type="italic">NME</i>直播博客，了解格拉斯顿伯里发生的所有最新动态</a>。</p></div></div><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/social-media-reacts-to-awful-shania-twain-set-at-glastonbury-2024-3770637">社交媒体对 2024 年格拉斯顿伯里音乐节“糟糕”的仙妮亚·唐恩 (Shania Twain) 的反应的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
格拉斯顿伯里 2024 年：帕洛玛·费思 (Paloma Faith) 在金字塔舞台上翻唱艾米·怀恩豪斯 (Amy Winehouse) https://www.nme.com/news/music/paloma-faith-covers-amy-winehouse-triumphant-pyramid-stage-set-3770605?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=paloma-faith-covers-amy-winehouse-胜利金字塔舞台布景Adam EnglandSun, 30 Jun 2024 14:36:41 +0000 Music NewsNewsPop https://www.nme.com/?p=3770605 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Paloma-Faith-Glasto.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="帕洛玛·费丝" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Paloma-Faith-Glasto.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Paloma-Faith-Glasto-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Paloma-Faith-Glasto-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Paloma-Faith-Glasto-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Paloma-Faith-Glasto-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Paloma-Faith-Glasto-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> “我们爱你，艾米，你精神在这里”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/paloma-faith-covers-amy-winehouse-triumphant-pyramid-stage-set-3770605">格拉斯顿伯里 2024 年后：Paloma Faith 在胜利的 Pyramid Stage 演出中翻唱 Amy Winehouse，</a>首先在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上发表。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Paloma-Faith-Glasto.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="帕洛玛·费丝" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Paloma-Faith-Glasto.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Paloma-Faith-Glasto-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Paloma-Faith-Glasto-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Paloma-Faith-Glasto-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Paloma-Faith-Glasto-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Paloma-Faith-Glasto-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/paloma-faith">帕洛玛·费斯 (Paloma Faith)</a>在<a href="https://www.nme.com/glastonbury-2024">2024 年格拉斯顿伯</a>里音乐节上打造了自己的金字塔舞台，并以“Back To Black”封面向<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/amy-winehouse">艾米·怀恩豪斯 (Amy Winehouse)</a>致敬。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/glastonbury-2024-liveblog-news-updates-reviews-rumours-photo-video-3769371">格拉斯顿伯里 2024 年现场博客：周日发生的所有活动</a><br /></strong></li></ul><p>Faith 的格拉斯顿伯里演出从今天下午（6 月 30 日）13:45 到 14:45，在<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/seasick-steve">晕船的史蒂夫</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/shania-twain">仙妮亚·唐恩</a>的表演之间进行。</p><p> Faith 首先翻唱了 Cass Elliott 的《Make Your Own Kind of Music》，然后说道：“艾米，我们爱你，你精神在这里”，然后开始演绎 Winehouse 2007 年的热门单曲。</p><p> Faith 在二月份发行的最新专辑《Glorification of Sadness》中演唱了第二首单曲《Bad Woman》后，她发表了一次强调的演讲，将这首歌献给单身妈妈：“我知道这很难，我正在做！”她说，哀叹女孩们被告知“做一个好女孩，永远守规矩”，[因为]这是不对的。我是一个坏女人，但我很自豪，我希望你能把你的女儿也培养成坏女人。”</p><p>在她的整个演出过程中，舞台上感觉就像一场派对气氛，许多伴唱、音乐家和舞者都穿着黑色和红色的服装，费思在她的唱片中一路走来，带领音乐节观众踏上她标志性的深情爵士流行音乐之旅。</p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="550" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">帕洛玛·菲丝 (Paloma Faith) 翻唱艾米·怀恩豪斯 (Amy Winehouse) 的《Back To Black》，这首歌太棒了</p><p>- didyoujustsaywig (@2002scoobydoo) <a href="https://twitter.com/2002scoobydoo/status/1807402029897130125?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">2024 年 6 月 30 日</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="550" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">帕洛玛为艾米唱回黑色，我在哭泣，这就是一切<img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/15.0.3/72x72/1f979.png" alt="🥹" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /><img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/15.0.3/72x72/1f979.png" alt="🥹" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /><img src="https://s.