39;任逍遥&#39;</strong><br /> <strong>“运动裤”</strong><br /> <strong>&#39;倒挂&#39;</strong><br /> <strong>“不能依赖你”</strong><br /> <strong>&#39;催眠曲&#39;</strong><br /> <strong>“改变”</strong><br /> <strong>“只有爱才会如此伤害”</strong> </p><div class="td_block_wrap tdb_single_content tdi_86 td-pb-border-top td_block_template_2 td-post-content tagdiv-type" data-td-block-uid="tdi_86" data-io-article-url="https://www.nme.com/news/music/coldplay-honour-michael-eavis-and-michael-j-fox-at-glastonbury-2024-3770369"><div class="tdb-block-inner td-fix-index"><div class="td_block_wrap tdb_single_content tdi_86 td-pb-border-top td_block_template_2 td-post-content tagdiv-type" data-td-block-uid="tdi_86" data-io-article-url="https://www.nme.com/news/music/glastonbury-2024-the-last-dinner-party-speak-on-the-general-election-encourage-voters-to-have-some-fucking-empathy-3770181"><div class="tdb-block-inner td-fix-index"><p> <a class="c-link c-link--focus-visible" href="https://www.nme.com/glastonbury-2024" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" data-stringify-link="https://www.nme.com/glastonbury-2024" data-sk="tooltip_parent">请返回<i data-stringify-type="italic">NME</i> ，了解 2024 年格拉斯顿伯里音乐节的最新</a>新闻、评论、采访、照片、谣言等。请<a class="c-link c-link--focus-visible" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/glastonbury-2024-liveblog-news-updates-reviews-rumours-photo-video-3769371" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" data-stringify-link="https://www.nme.com/news/music/glastonbury-2024-liveblog-news-updates-reviews-rumours-photo-video-3769371" data-sk="tooltip_parent">在此处查看<i data-stringify-type="italic">NME</i>直播博客，了解格拉斯顿伯里发生的所有最新动态</a>。</p></div></div></div></div><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/paloma-faith-covers-amy-winehouse-triumphant-pyramid-stage-set-3770605">格拉斯顿伯里 2024 年之后：Paloma Faith 在胜利的 Pyramid Stage 演出中翻唱 Amy Winehouse，</a>首先在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上发表。</p> ;
